{"id":66919,"title":"Prostate cancer: predicting high-risk prostate cancer-a novel stratification tool.","abstract":"Currently, numerous systems exist for the identification of high-risk prostate cancer, but few of these systems can guide treatment strategies. A new stratification tool that uses common diagnostic factors can help to predict outcomes after radical prostatectomy. The tool aids physicians in the identification of appropriate candidates for aggressive, local treatment.","date":"2014-05-14","categories":"Male Urogenital Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24662730","annotations":[{"name":"Physician","weight":0.657965,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physician"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.62,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.603867,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Prostate cancer","weight":0.357874,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prostate_cancer"},{"name":"Aggression","weight":0.233385,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aggression"},{"name":"Prostatectomy","weight":0.158474,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prostatectomy"},{"name":"Novel","weight":0.147465,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novel"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.0551856,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Prostate","weight":0.0546925,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prostate"},{"name":"Prediction","weight":0.0311179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prediction"},{"name":"Tool","weight":0.0297435,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tool"},{"name":"Strategy","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy"},{"name":"Identity document","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Identity_document"},{"name":"Social stratification","weight":0.0147415,"wikiped